[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    325[0m:[38;5;10m[49m | A2 | HIGH | Architecture | Step 5, performance benchmarks table | Offline policy evaluation methodology unspecified. Performance claims (2-5% TCP improvement, 8-15% NTCP reduction) are presented without explaining how they were computed or what assumptions they rest on. | Add focused paragraph on OPE approaches. State that benchmarks are simulator-based estimates. Acknowledge that real-world validation requires prospective trials. |
