[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    343[0m:[38;5;10m[49m 1. **Fix A1 (CRITICAL):** Restructure safety constraint discussion to clearly separate soft constraints (training-time shaping) from hard constraints (inference-time verification). This is a patient safety issue and the single most important fix.
